    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Spectacles of any kind that end in a point on the upper outside rim. Initially popular for women in the 1950s and 1960s, the shape goes in and out of fashion.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
